Rating: 4
A 4 with several modifications. I used a fresh chicken broth to which I added some fresh ginger and the greens of my leaks (well washed). I added some chili powder and garam masala when simmering the final product...Then I garnished with the no fat yogurt, some chopped ciantro, some more garam masala...and a squeeze of fresh lime. That's how it became a 4!!!

