I chose this recipe because it was so healthy, but was pleasantly surprised to find it very tasty as well. I used nonfat milk (1 cup) and a splash of fat free half and half - didn't have 2% on hand.

Rating: 2
I found this soup to be watery, bland, and lacking in dimension. It needed alot of doctoring, such as the addition of chicken broth, ALOT more curry, and some onion powder. To be fair, my husband and brother liked it and had seconds. It might be better prepared with chicken broth instead of water.

